README: BLUEPRINT FTP AREA
ftp://ftp.bind.ca/pub/BIND/spec/w3schema/


LAST UPDATE OF THIS README: February 2, 2005


This directory contains the BIND specification v3.1 in W3C XML Schema format. 
Files are released as indicated on their data/timestamp.


FILES---------------------------------------------------------------------------

bind.xsd            Mail BIND specification

bind-config.xsd     BIND web configuration specification

bindprof.xsd        BIND profile specification

import              Directory containing BIND dependant NCBI Schemas.  These 
                    schemas should be included in bind.xsd for proper XML 
                    validation.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

